title: Steve King
deleted: In August 1, 2015 a Republican Iowa Senator [[Steve King]] quoted - “after gay marriage was done legally, you can now marry your [[lawnmower]]“. An individual did in fact try to do just that, but was in fact automatically rejected by a [[county clerk]] in Iowa.<ref>[https://archive.thinkprogress.org/if-you-want-to-marry-your-lawnmower-steve-king-believes-thats-now-legal-a6cd48951784/]</ref>
